environmentalDataLogging.entities

Class Measurement

  • java.lang.Object
    • environmentalDataLogging.entities.BaseEntity
      • environmentalDataLogging.entities.Measurement

  • @Entity
public class Measurement
extends BaseEntity
    The Measurement entity class is the link to the measurement table in the EnviroDB database. A Measurement contains all the information relating to the measurement of a sample.
